{
 "name": "RPlog_Kidnapped_on_GDIStar",
 "title": "Kidnapped on GDIStar",
 "summary": "In a lounge aboard the Corporate Sector station GDIStar, the CSA delegate Piper Drake chats with the Mon Calamari N'Saldon and the young Horansi Kuxli when the Imperial Admiral Sabbath joins them, holding forth on the coming upheaval in the Empire and trading a long debate with N'Saldon over wealth, morality, and service. After the others drift off, Sabbath corners Piper in the residential sector and calmly informs her that she will accompany him as a hostage to his meeting with a Grand Moff, confiscating her comlink despite N'Saldon's overheard alarm. He marches her through weapons scans to his shuttle, the Crazy Diamond, and flies her to his starship the Ummagumma, where he settles the frightened delegate in the crew lounge -- insisting she think of him not as her captor but her host for the week or two ahead.",
